  "html": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">In this video explanation, we focus on the correct use of <strong>この,&nbsp;</strong><strong>その,&nbsp;</strong><strong>あの</strong>.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><strong>この (This)</strong> - close to the speaker, <strong>その (</strong><strong>T</strong><strong>hat)</strong> - close to the listener, <strong>あの</strong> <strong>(</strong><strong>T</strong><strong>hat over there)&nbsp;</strong>- far from both people.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Please pay attention to the distance of the speakers and the object.</span></p><div class=\"fr-view\"><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/bq847qehra84otn6gic0\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D2 L2 Explanation.mp4 - 00:14\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span><br></p></div>",
